<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Happy Birthday Pari</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(#ffccdd, #ffe6f2);
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      text-align: center;
    }h1 {
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  margin-top: 40px;
  color: #ff1470;
  animation: pop 1s ease forwards;
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255,0,120,0.4);
}

@keyframes pop {
  0% { transform: scale(0); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); }
}

/* Floating hearts */
.heart {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -150px;
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  background: pink;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  animation: floatUp 7s infinite ease-in;
}
.heart:before, .heart:after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  background: pink;
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.heart:before { top: -15px; left: 0; }
.heart:after { left: -15px; top: 0; }

.heart:nth-child(1) { left: 20%; animation-delay: 0s; }
.heart:nth-child(2) { left: 50%; animation-delay: 2s; }
.heart:nth-child(3) { left: 80%; animation-delay: 4s; }

@keyframes floatUp {
  0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(45deg); opacity: 1; }
  50% { transform: translateY(-400px) rotate(45deg); opacity: 0.6; }
  100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(45deg); opacity: 1; }
}

/* Letter box */
.letter-box {
  width: 85%;
  max-width: 650px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  background: white;
  padding: 25px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(255,0,120,0.3);
  animation: fadeIn 2s ease forwards;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Photos */
.photos {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.photos img {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

p {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: #444;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>  <h1>💖 Happy Birthday My Love Pari 💖</h1>  <div class="heart"></div>
  <div class="heart"></div>
  <div class="heart"></div>  <div class="letter-box">
    <h2>My Sweetest Pari ❤️</h2><div class="photos">
  <img src="https://i.ibb.co/7S6S9zq/romantic1.jpg" />
  <img src="https://i.ibb.co/4f7hYHz/romantic2.jpg" />
  <img src="https://i.ibb.co/Xb5XXzW/romantic3.jpg" />
</div>

<p>
  Pari, you are the most beautiful part of my life. Every moment with you feels like magic,
  every conversation feels like a warm hug, and every smile of yours makes my heart melt.
</p>

<p>
  I never believed someone could mean this much to me… until you came into my world.
  You are not just someone I love — you are my peace, my happiness, my reason to smile.
</p>

<p>
  On your birthday, I want to promise you something — as long as my heart beats,
  it beats for you. As long as my eyes see, they will search only for you.
  As long as I exist, my love will be yours.
</p>

<p>
  I wish this year blesses you with all the joy you bring into my life.
  You deserve endless happiness, comfort, and love.
</p>

<p>
  Happiest Birthday, my love. You are my forever. 💞✨
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.4rem;">
  With all my love,<br/>Aditya ❤️
</p>

  </div>  <!-- Background music -->  <audio autoplay loop>
    <source src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/download/audio/2022/03/15/audio_7f3bcb9e4e.mp3?filename=romantic-melody-20767.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
  </audio>  <!-- Fireworks animation -->  <script>
    const createFirework = () => {
      const fw = document.createElement('div');
      fw.className = 'firework';
      document.body.appendChild(fw);
      setTimeout(() => fw.remove(), 1500);
    };
    setInterval(createFirework, 800);
  </script>  <style>
    .firework {
      position: fixed;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: calc(50% - 4px);
      left: calc(50% - 4px);
      animation: explode 1.5s ease-out forwards;
    }

    @keyframes explode {
      0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(40); opacity: 0; }
    }

    /* Touch hearts effect */
    body { position: relative; }
    .touch-heart {
      position: absolute;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background: red;
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      opacity: 0.8;
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: vanish 1s ease-out forwards;
    }
    .touch-heart:before, .touch-heart:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background: red;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .touch-heart:before { top: -10px; left: 0; }
    .touch-heart:after { left: -10px; top: 0; }

    @keyframes vanish {
      0% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) rotate(45deg); }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(3) rotate(45deg); }
    }
  </style>  <script>
    document.addEventListener('touchstart', e => {
      const heart = document.createElement('div');
      heart.className = 'touch-heart';
      heart.style.left = e.touches[0].clientX + 'px';
      heart.style.top = e.touches[0].clientY + 'px';
      document.body.appendChild(heart);
      setTimeout(() => heart.remove(), 1000);
    });
  </script></body>
</html>
